# Input

```css
/* Media features in parentheses */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
    .container {
        width: 750px;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
        width: 100%;
    }
}

/* Boolean features */
@media (color) {
    body {
        background: white;
    }
}

@media (hover) {
    a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
}

/* Range syntax */
@media (width >= 600px) {
    .wide {
        display: block;
    }
}

@media (400px <= width <= 700px) {
    .medium {
        display: flex;
    }
}

/* Combinators */
@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .tablet {
        font-size: 14px;
    }
}

@media (orientation: portrait) or (orientation: landscape) {
    .responsive {
        display: grid;
    }
}

/* Negation */
@media not (color) {
    body {
        background: gray;
    }
}

@media not (hover) {
    a {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
}

/* Nested conditions */
@media ((min-width: 400px) and (max-width: 800px)) or (orientation: portrait) {
    .complex {
        padding: 10px;
    }
}

/* Print media */
@media print and (min-resolution: 300dpi) {
    .print-only {
        display: block;
    }
}

```


